      "text": "舍不得离开",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 4.369,
      "time_str": "00:04.369",
      "text": "眼泪掉下来",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 7.24,
      "time_str": "00:07.240",
      "text": "我的爱花败",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 10.24,
      "time_str": "00:10.240",
      "text": "何时开",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 12.49,
      "time_str": "00:12.490",
      "text": "想要的痛快",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 15.99,
      "time_str": "00:15.990",
      "text": "原来的一种伤害",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 19.2,
      "time_str": "00:19.200",
      "text": "难道是上天安排",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 22.3,
      "time_str": "00:22.300",
      "text": "不让我们相爱",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 26.04,
      "time_str": "00:26.040",
      "text": "是怪我把爱想得太天真",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 28.8,
      "time_str": "00:28.800",
      "text": "还是我们有情没缘分",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 31.727,
      "time_str": "00:31.727",
      "text": "到头来爱情伤了两个人",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.199,
      "time_str": "00:34.199",
      "text": "这个故事没有了下文",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 37.88,
      "time_str": "00:37.880",
      "text": "就在那个美丽的黄昏",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 40.3,
      "time_str": "00:40.300",
      "text": "印下最后一个吻",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 42.727,
      "time_str": "00:42.727",
      "text": "让我一个人在夜里体味余温",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 46.49,
      "time_str": "00:46.490",
      "text": "忘记已经是个局外人",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 49.468,
      "time_str": "00:49.468",
      "text": "就连我最爱喝的冰咖啡",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 52.37,
      "time_str": "00:52.370",
      "text": "竟然淡的没有了滋味",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 55.79,
      "time_str": "00:55.790",
      "text": "再也听不到暧昧的责备",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.337,
      "time_str": "00:57.337",
      "text": "从此身边没有你依偎",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 60.398,
      "time_str": "01:00.398",
      "text": "曾经的生气斗嘴究竟错与对",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 63.66,
      "time_str": "01:03.660",
      "text": "都已无所谓",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 66.339,
      "time_str": "01:06.339",
      "text": "我们不得不该",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 69.219,
      "time_str": "01:09.219",
      "text": "放弃这份错爱",
